data.description: This turnkey three-bedroom, two-bath home, built in 2019 by Option One Builders, exudes modern luxury and practicality. A new roof enhances both aesthetic appeal and structural integrity. The outdoor oasis features a custom heated saltwater pool and spa, with all new equipment, heated by both solar and an electric unit, fully secured with electric storm shutters in the rear and accordion shutters encircling the rest of the home, providing both tranquility and safety. Inside,Tile flooring throughout with a large kitchen that boasts granite countertops. The oversized side two-car garage adds practical convenience, while new exterior paint revitalizes the home's curb appeal. Situated on Palmetto Pines Country Club's driving range in Cape Coral, this property offers scenic views and an immersive lifestyle for golf enthusiasts. Notably, there's no homeowners association (HOA) or flood insurance, granting residents the freedom to personalize their living experience without the added costs. This meticulously designed home stands as an ideal choice for those seeking a sophisticated, secure, and independent lifestyle in Cape Coral.
